      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/uk-bond-sale-to-gauge-investor-appetite-after-market-turmoil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国自上周市场动荡以来首次发行债券，此举有望反映出投资者对英国政府债券的兴趣。]]></description>
